I had to make a quick stop at wally world. I arrived to find a line up. WHATTTTTTTTTTTTTTTT. So asked whats up bud? Lined up for the new, old style nintendo. WHATTTTTTTTTTTTTTT  Heres the kicker. 60 people lined up. Only 3 games in the store. They were handing out rain checks. I was in and out with my shaving cream and deoderant. LOL
Did you want to smell and look good while tying roe bags?
